# ADCopyParameters - Changelog

## [1.1.0] - 2026-03-04
- added a context menu option for knobs : "Copy to Selected"

## [1.0.3] - 2026-03-04
- logger is now set to INFO

## [1.0.2] - 2026-03-02
- Fix the addon not registering shortcut since changes in 1.0.1
- Now using a custom QEvent filter for tracking the LMB with a 0.5 seconds buffer
- Improved knob file type handling

## [1.0.1] - 2026-03-02
- Fix the addon activating on random alt shortcuts.

## [1.0.0] - 2026-03-01
- Initial release.
- Alt+click on any knob copies its value to the matching knob on all other selected nodes.